opennlp.ccg.perceptron
Interface FeatureVector.Iterator

Enclosing interface:
FeatureVector
public static interface FeatureVector.Iterator

Iterator over feature-value pairs. Features and values must be retrieved using a pair of calls to nextFeature and nextValue, otherwise the behavior is not defined.
